    "Sourcing limited to job boards and LinkedIn InMail blasts with low response rates on passive candidates.",
    "Passive candidate nurture is manual, inconsistent, and drops off after initial outreach attempts.",
    "No unified view of candidate interactions across channels, leading to duplicate outreach and poor candidate experience."
  ],
  "agentification": [
    "Multi-channel intelligent sourcing across internal databases, professional networks, and talent communities.",
    "Personalized outreach sequences tailored to candidate profiles, career interests, and engagement signals.",
    "Automated passive candidate nurture campaigns with adaptive timing and content based on response patterns."
