        "label": "Multi-Channel Search",
        "description": "Intelligent candidate identification across LinkedIn, Indeed, and internal databases. Gemini scores candidate-role fit beyond keyword matching."
      },
      {
        "label": "Personalized Outreach",
        "description": "AI-crafted outreach sequences tailored to candidate backgrounds, career interests, and engagement signals. Adaptive timing and follow-up."
